navigate("/Patient")} previousPage> Back to start navigate("/GPServices")} nextPage> GP Services Profile Name {data.fullName} navigate("/NameChangeStart")} children="Change"/> D.O.B {data.dob} navigate("/DOBChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Gender {data.gender} navigate("/GenderChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Address {data.address} navigate("/AddressChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Email {data.email} navigate("/EmailChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Contact No. Fetched data of Contact No. navigate("/NumberChangeStart")} children="Change"/> Password ************* navigate("/PasswordChangeStart")} children="Change"/>
); } export default Profile;
